pastoral
Homonym Number:
Word Class:adjective
Sense Number:2
Definition:
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: pertaining to or engaged in stock raising, usu sheep farming, as distinct from 'agricultural' farming, ie arable farming or cropping
